This paper is about improving word embeddings, which is a common task in natural language processing (NLP). The most relevant sub-category for this paper is likely cs.CL (Computation and Language), which focuses on NLP and related tasks. Additionally, the use of post-processing algorithms and dimensionality reduction techniques suggests that this paper could also be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
